latestIgtvVideos.title: Let’s do some lip care routine today!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Lipkit is specially formulated for pigmentation of lips and for dry lips.
This kit include 3 products Formulated to tackle these issues.
As we wear lipsticks on a day to day basis there is higher chances of getting lip pigmentation.
Sundamage is also another reason.
I have been trying this lipkit from @wild_organica_home for a while now.
It works really good and it is made of natural ingredients only.
Lipbalm is made with coffee infused almond oil , beetroot infused avacado oil and with cocoa and Shea butter.
It helps to reduce lip pigmentation and it prevents dryness of lips.
It hydrates and moisturizes well.

Lipscrub is to exfoliate lips to remove dead skin cells and to prevent further pigmentation.

Lipmask is made from sugarcane straw ash which helps to reduce pigmentation and it is very hydrating on lips.

You can visit thier website or Instagram to place your orders @wild_organica_home 

Website-http://www.wildorganicahome.com

A legacy reborn in Trivandrum ✨

Step into the beautifully restored Fabindia store at Sasthamangalam, nestled inside a heritage building from the 1940s. With traditional wooden pillars, vintage charm, and earthy interiors, this space is more than a store — it’s a celebration of India’s diverse craftsmanship.

From Ajrakh, Dabu prints and Chikankari embroidery, discover handcrafted treasures from across the country. Explore signature handloom sarees, elegant Indian wear, stylish menswear, and thoughtfully curated home décor — all under one heritage roof.

Come visit the Sasthamangalam store and shop the crafts of India, all in one immersive experience.

📍Sasthamangalam, Trivandrum

latestPosts.caption:
Happy Mother’s Day to all the incredible mothers out there.
To the ones who fill our lives with love, warmth, and strength — today is for you.

And a special salute to the brave mothers whose sons and daughters stand at the borders, guarding our nation with courage and honor. Your sacrifices, silent prayers, and unshakable strength deserve the deepest respect.

To every mother — whether near or far, in uniform or in spirit — thank you for being the heart of our world.

Wishing you a Mother’s Day filled with love, peace, and pride.
Jai Hind.
